Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Symbolism=The Worship of Images
  - Combat-Action=Metanoia=The Inversion of Values
By: Hermes
---
As bodies are reflected in mirrors, so incorporeal things are
reflected in bodies, and the intelligible Kosmos is reflected in the
sensible Kosmos. Therefore, my King, worship the statues of the gods,
seeing that these statues too have in them forms which come from the
intelligible Kosmos.
